title: Hard Reset Redux (2.1.0.3)-GOG
description:
Hard Reset Redux (c) Gambitious Digital Entertainment

Release Date : 07/2016
Protection : -
Discs : 1
Game Version : 1.1.1.0
Genre : Action
Languages : EN/FR/DE/PL/RU

The acclaimed First-Person Shooter returns fully upgraded, and more
beautifully challenging than ever. Hard Reset Redux is a brand new
version of the cyberpunk classic that includes all the content of
previous editions, and adds new improved gameplay, enhanced visuals
and additional content to make this the Definitive Edition of Hard
Reset. Hard Reset Redux is an action-packed and hardcore single-
player shooter which embraces the best qualities that the genre has
it offer.

For more info go to : https://www.gog.com/game/hard_reset_redux
